Interface EndianInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjectEndianInputStream, ObjectEndianOutputStream

    public interface EndianInterface
extends java.io.Serializable
    This interface defines what we expect from an input or output object to handle both Little as Big Endian.
    Since:
    JDK 1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
